WEBVTT

01:41.628 --> 01:46.698
1995-08-24 Public Program, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil

01:47.043 --> 01:51.910
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

01:54.824 --> 02:01.713
At the very outset, I have to say truth is what it is.

02:01.914 --> 02:07.691
You cannot change it; you cannot transform it.

02:07.892 --> 02:14.059
You cannot describe it, but you have to experience it.

02:19.497 --> 02:22.827
Whatever I am going to tell you here today,

02:23.028 --> 02:27.821
you need not take it for granted.

02:28.022 --> 02:34.741
We have had lots of problems with blind faith.

02:34.942 --> 02:39.312
So, whatever I am saying, if it is proved,

02:39.513 --> 02:43.826
then you have to accept it.

02:44.027 --> 02:48.540
Because it is for your benevolence,

02:48.741 --> 02:54.895
for the benevolence of your family, benevolence of your country

02:55.096 --> 03:00.382
and benevolence of the whole World.

03:04.275 --> 03:12.106
If you see in modern times, people are very restless.

03:12.307 --> 03:15.919
And there is no peace within.

03:16.695 --> 03:23.281
This restlessness starts when you try to find the truth.

03:24.166 --> 03:28.021
You may not be aware of it.

03:28.222 --> 03:32.104
But it exists.

03:33.509 --> 03:39.327
I am very happy to see so many people here in Brazil,

03:39.527 --> 03:44.775
in Rio, who are seeking the truth.

03:45.656 --> 03:54.244
At the very outset, again, I would
like to tell you what is the truth.

03:54.445 --> 03:59.031
The first thing is when you say this is my body,

03:59.232 --> 04:02.626
these are my hands, this is my intelligence,

04:02.827 --> 04:07.788
we talk of ‘my, my, my!’

04:08.154 --> 04:12.824
But who is the owner of this 'I'.

04:13.025 --> 04:18.314
This owner is your spirit.

04:24.275 --> 04:29.154
Actually, you are not this body, this mind, you are not your emotions,

04:24.511 --> 04:30.094
your intelligence, you are not your ego and your conditionings

04:30.302 --> 04:35.392
but you are pure spirit.

04:35.593 --> 04:39.252
Unless and until you become,

04:39.453 --> 04:47.790
unless and until you become the
spirit, you are going to be restless.

04:47.991 --> 04:54.454
That is what Christ has said, that you have to be born again.

04:54.655 --> 05:02.245
It is not like branding yourself "I am
born again", but it’s an experience.

05:02.446 --> 05:06.448
And you become the spirit.

05:06.649 --> 05:12.863
And you get all the powers of the spirit.

05:13.064 --> 05:18.494
There is another truth, which we have to know about.

05:18.695 --> 05:24.946
You see all this beautiful flowers, it’s a miracle.

05:25.147 --> 05:31.240
But they take it, take them for granted, you take them for granted.

05:32.966 --> 05:37.865
And we never think how they have been created.

05:38.438 --> 05:44.076
We don’t know anything about the living process.

05:44.630 --> 05:52.303
For example, if you ask a doctor who runs your heart,

05:52.511 --> 05:58.288
he’ll say it is an autonomous nervous system.

06:45.326 --> 06:51.146
So, you can ask who is this auto?

06:51.625 --> 06:56.094
In the same way, I have to tell you that

06:56.295 --> 07:03.480
there is all pervading power of divine love,

07:04.135 --> 07:07.982
which is a subtle energy.

07:08.208 --> 07:12.068
Which does all the living work.

07:12.269 --> 07:20.233
It has also done our evolution and we have come to this human level.

07:20.434 --> 07:26.296
But at this human level, we live in a world which is relative,

07:26.497 --> 07:30.570
it is not absolute.

07:31.405 --> 07:36.622
Why we have to know the absolute truth?

07:36.823 --> 07:41.709
Once we have an absolute truth, then there will be no quarrel,

07:41.910 --> 07:45.962
no fights, no wars.

07:46.507 --> 07:55.200
And all of them, all of you, will know the same truth.

07:55.401 --> 08:00.505
This is what has happened so far that everybody thinks

08:00.706 --> 08:03.455
this is the truth and another one thinks this is the truth,

08:03.656 --> 08:07.593
and they are just fighting.

08:08.286 --> 08:13.980
No religion is exclusive, you should understand this point.

08:14.181 --> 08:20.995
When Christ came, He talked about Abraham and about Moses.

08:21.196 --> 08:26.167
So it was not exclusive religion He established.

08:26.368 --> 08:30.071
Then came Mohammed Sahib, he talked about Abraham,

08:30.272 --> 08:37.835
about Moses, about Christ, also about
the Mother of Christ with great respect.

08:38.036 --> 08:42.935
So, Islam is also not an exclusive religion.

08:43.159 --> 08:50.870
The growth of spiritual life is described in every incarnation like that.

08:51.071 --> 08:57.095
But now we are fighting in the name of God.

08:57.296 --> 09:03.254
Not only that, but among the Christians, among the Muslims,

09:03.455 --> 09:08.881
among the Jews, they are fighting among each other.

09:09.082 --> 09:11.155
But once you know the absolute truth,

09:11.356 --> 09:17.082
then you realize that all these religions came on this Earth,

09:17.283 --> 09:22.740
as beautiful fowers of one tree of spirituality,

09:22.941 --> 09:26.733
at different times.

09:26.934 --> 09:34.918
And now we have plucked the flowers
and fighting with the dead flowers,

09:35.119 --> 09:38.658
bringing bad name to all those great incarnations

09:38.859 --> 09:44.127
who came on this Earth to save us.

09:46.661 --> 09:54.773
So, as it is, [inaudible]

09:54.974 --> 10:03.472
you have been already described about the
subtle system we have within ourselves.

10:03.680 --> 10:08.334
That works out this ascent.

10:08.535 --> 10:18.185
This triangular bone is called as the sacrum,
where this power of Kundalini resides.

10:18.386 --> 10:24.783
That means the Greeks knew it was a sacred bone.

10:24.984 --> 10:31.072
Now, this resides in every individual.

10:31.273 --> 10:35.632
She is your own individual mother.

10:35.833 --> 10:40.519
She knows everything about you.

10:40.720 --> 10:47.689
Like a tape recorder, she has taped all that you have aspired,

10:47.890 --> 10:53.669
