10:54.716 --> 10:58.936
So, it’s your own power,

10:59.137 --> 11:03.151
which is to be awakened.

11:03.352 --> 11:11.988
It is like a seed which is put in the
Mother Earth and sprouts by itself.

11:13.636 --> 11:22.993
Now, the problem is that you have to understand that

11:23.194 --> 11:28.622
