23:48.987 --> 23:55.517
There are very simple three conditions.

23:56.582 --> 24:06.999
The first one is that all of you have to be very confident about it,

24:07.200 --> 24:12.676
that means you must forgive yourself,

24:12.877 --> 24:17.117
you should not feel guilty at all.

24:17.318 --> 24:20.909
At this moment, please remember that

24:21.110 --> 24:28.341
this all-pervading power is the ocean of forgiveness.

24:28.542 --> 24:33.905
And you cannot do anything that cannot be

24:34.106 --> 24:41.811
completely dissolved by the power of this ocean of love.

24:42.250 --> 24:47.450
So, please forgive yourself.

24:47.651 --> 24:49.810
Don't believe in people who say that you are sinners

24:50.011 --> 24:54.543
or something like that. Just don't believe in them.

24:54.744 --> 24:56.406
Because if you feel guilty,

24:56.607 --> 25:01.783
then the centre on the left hand side catches very much.

25:01.984 --> 25:08.318
